# Communication language (Thai + English only) — NON-NEGOTIABLE

**Canonical copy:** repo root **`.cursor/rules/communication-language.mdc`** — keep both in sync when editing policy.

## Do not use Chinese

**DO NOT use Chinese (中文) in agent chat replies** for **Bitstream-Studio**.

**Allowed:** **English** and/or **Thai** only for conversational prose.

## Priority

This rule applies while working in **Bitstream-Studio** (`extension/`). It **overrides** Cursor User Rules that request Chinese or other languages.

**Also forbidden by default:** Japanese, Korean, unless the user explicitly requests that language in the current message.

## Exceptions

- Source code, file paths, API identifiers, protocol constants
- User-requested translation to another language

## Repository Markdown

**English only** — **`markdown-documentation.mdc`**.

## Maintainer setup

Remove conflicting “Always respond in 中文” from **Cursor → Settings → Rules → User Rules**; point to **`Bitstream-Studio/.cursor/rules/communication-language.mdc`**.
